Question: Explain to your grandmother how to use her smartphone to find new restaurant in her area.
Answer:
this is a simple task if you follow my steps. first of all, click the icon with the name of google map. after it launches, click the triangle button at the right down corner, it will show your current position. lastly, click the dot which represents your current position a little bit longer, a textbox will show up. type in new restaurants nearby. google map will show you all newly opened restaurants arround you. click the dot you are interested for more information. 